Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:42.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99495,102290}I never imagined\Nthat this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103416,106169}That's right. I forgot\Nthat girls walk slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:49.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108171,109589}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109881,112133}Oh, no. No need to apologize…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:53.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112717,113676}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117221,118181}I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:01.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119766,121309}By the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121893,123853}I'd like to make it clear…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:05.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123978,125605}…there won't be any\Nof that daily diary exchange…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:07.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125730,127523}…or using a beeper business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:08.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127982,128983}Needless to say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129067,130360}…there won't be any\Nmatching clothes either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130526,131569}And birthdays…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131653,134364}…Christmas, Valentine's Day…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135198,136366}…I don't…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:18.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138034,138993}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140578,142955}I don't want anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155551,157053}I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:43.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158971,163351}A FORMIDABLE FOE?!\NA MISCHIEVOUS PIXIE'S TRAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171317,172318}Again…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:55.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173361,175113}I discovered\Nthat this is the house…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175279,176656}…of the Mysterious Thief Lucifer…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176948,179575}…who is Eimi Haneoka.\NSince monitoring this house…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180410,181369}…Lucifer hasn't shown…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181452,183329}…any movement…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183871,186582}…but her daughter\Nsometimes goes out at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188084,190461}And every time she goes out,\Nthe next morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191421,193631}…there's an article about St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195216,197176}Does this mean…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:22.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199053,202223}Hey! Look! Look at the article\Nabout St. Tail this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202890,205017}She escaped\Nfrom you again, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205184,207270}Because he has Meimi now…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207770,210648}He doesn't care about St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211774,213276}Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213401,214819}Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214986,217029}What kind of logic is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217155,218364}Nothing has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218781,221325}I will definitely catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221951,224328}You want to impress Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224412,225955}I see…!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226038,227582}Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228207,230001}Why are you jumping\Nto all of these conclusions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230543,232712}How about this, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233629,236090}It's the fortune teller.\NI've heard she is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236257,237258}A fortune teller?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237383,239510}Oh, yeah. I've heard that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240011,243347}Yeah, why don't you ask her\Nabout the location of St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245224,246934}That's a cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247518,249228}What he really wants to know is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:13.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249812,253357}…how their relationship is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253983,256652}Right! This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257361,259572}Let it go! Let's change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259906,261324}You guys…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261407,263367}Don't get mad!\NWe're happy for the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263576,266662}That's right!\NFinally you two got together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271083,272084}Takamiya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273211,275463}How could she, Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275755,277590}How could she choose\NAsuka over me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278299,280718}Why? Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:43.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280802,283304}Hey! Get away\Nfrom me, Saruwatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284347,285640}What's wrong…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288684,290561}It's unusual to see you here…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291395,292730}Mimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293773,296150}I came here to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298903,301405}Boy! I can't even have\Na broken heart in peace…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310289,311582}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311791,312834}Nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314252,316254}I'm impressed, Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:20.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319674,320758}What else can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321634,324220}First of all, those two took…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325054,326764}…too long to get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326973,330226}Oh, I see. So half of it\Nwas stubborn pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330560,331727}Oh, brother…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336774,339694}I'm sure you'll have\NGod's blessings, Takamiya…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340444,341445}God's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342488,343656}It hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344156,345950}My beautiful face…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352498,353833}When I'm hitting him…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353958,355918}…I feel good.\NThat's interesting…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356919,358754}That's terrible…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359130,360965}So God's blessings…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:02.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361591,362884}…may not be necessary…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363217,364176}FORTUNE TELLING
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364260,365469}We've found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365970,368890}This is the fortune teller's house\Nthat Kyoko was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:18.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374937,378983}You aren't interested in this\Nkind of stuff. Let's forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381611,384655}Why don't you ask her\Nabout the location of St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385448,386449}That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387992,389660}You want to go in, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:32.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391954,392955}Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396542,397501}It's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403132,404300}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407011,408346}That's the girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409138,411057}Excuse me, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416562,417563}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:01.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417688,421734}I've just opened\Na fortune telling shop near this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422526,424153}Please come by\Nwith your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426280,428074}Oh, my…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428950,430493}Oh, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431410,434163}We've heard your fortunes\Nare very accurate…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435206,436165}You want to know…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436332,437375}…whether you are right\Nfor each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437667,438626}What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:19.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438834,439877}When I see you two, I can tell…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452974,455643}Your names and dates of birth…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457103,459939}Meimi Haneoka,\Nborn on September 29th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460147,461857}And Asuka Jr. is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:45.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462775,465027}Daiki Asuka, August 12th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466070,469699}So he is Asuka Jr.,\Nspecial agent for the mayor…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470574,472618}What are you going to do\Nwith the crystal ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472868,473828}Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497643,498602}Well…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:23.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500646,503649}A thick fog is\Nfilling the crystal ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504400,506193}So I can't see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511615,513576}I've never seen such thick fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514410,517413}And I can see a ring\Naround his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:41.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518289,521000}This must be\Nabout the secret promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521542,522960}It's a one-sided promise…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523210,527089}What? Is she talking\Nabout St. Tail and Asuka Jr?.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528132,531135}It seems the ring can\Nnever be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531594,533345}His character\Nand straightforwardness…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533554,534930}…is indicated in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535723,538392}As a result, this relationship…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539060,540394}…is doomed to failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541145,542188}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:06.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542897,546567}You're hiding something\Nvery big from him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548986,550488}I guess I've hit the bull's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:14.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553949,554909}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557495,559538}That's why I hate\Nfortune telling stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560039,562041}She knew things\Nwithout getting any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562541,565377}Listen! That's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566087,567254}Those who talk\Nnonsense and tell lies…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:28.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567379,568631}…are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570466,571425}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572968,574595}Honest eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575846,577473}Unremovable ring…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579100,581727}All right, then.\NLet's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582603,584230}I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:46.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585981,586941}That's the sign…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587108,589485}…that he can't forgive\Npeople who deceive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:53.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590069,593114}I'm sure he won't forgive\Nmy being St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:55.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594782,595741}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597076,599245}That's a solid-gold statue of Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600329,603332}Yesterday, a person\Nnamed Sakiko visited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603958,606001}She valued it a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607253,608212}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609296,610297}You know about Pandora…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610381,613092}…the fortune telling place,\Ndon't you, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613217,614176}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:18.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615344,618097}Sakiko went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621976,622977}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623227,624645}My statue of Mary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624937,625896}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626522,628774}That solid-gold statue of Mary…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628983,631610}…is bringing you misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632278,633237}No way…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636490,638993}You can bring\Nthe solid-gold statue…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639118,641120}…of Mary to us immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641662,643789}We'll take full responsibility\Nfor its disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645082,646959}You've got to be kidding!\NHow could I…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647543,650254}Are you prepared\Nto have misfortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652715,654675}I can't do it…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656135,657553}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662766,665144}So did she give it away? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:10.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665519,670191}I suppose\Nthe fortune teller uses hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:11.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670941,671901}Hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:15.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672359,675779}So Sakiko can't go to the police…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:17.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676947,677990}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678240,680034}– I went there.\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680159,681827}I went to the fortune teller…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681952,683704}…and she gave me\Na scary fortune…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:29.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684830,689001}If Asuka Jr. finds out I'm St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689919,692463}You've been deceiving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695341,696592}Let's stop stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699303,700304}Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709188,710314}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710856,713817}I appreciate what you\Nhave done very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714860,716111}But you don't need…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:12:00.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716237,720824}…to see Asuka Jr.\Nas St. Tail anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721992,723494}So let's end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726580,728457}I love you. I love you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728832,730960}No! We can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731543,733462}We can't desert those\Npeople who are in trouble…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734880,735839}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737841,740594}We have to get back\Nthe solid-gold statue of Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:27.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744056,747434}Now it's lunch time!\NLunch time! Lunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747935,750104}You brought a lunchbox\Ntoday, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751063,752064}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755818,756819}It's been a while…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756944,759154}…since St. Tail\Nbooby-trapped your lunchbox!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:44.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761115,764451}"Tonight I'll get\Nthe solid-gold statue of Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:45.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764660,765619}– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767204,770332}Oh, boy! She really\Nwent all out on this lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:51.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770708,771917}I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773335,776213}Hey, Haneoka.\NLook at Asuka's lunchbox…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776839,779842}– Stop it!\N– Then let us eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782803,785973}Let me make lots and lots\Nof whatever you like…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787224,788726}Whatever happens\Nfrom this point…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788726,789768}COOKBOOK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789810,791353}…I hope I have no regrets…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:22.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798902,802072}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807494,808454}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810998,811957}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:37.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814209,817087}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:51.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830351,831435}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833228,835147}Please tell me\Nwhen things get too painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835898,837274}Please promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838233,839568}If it happens…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840861,842446}If it happens, then I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842863,844365}…will become St. Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846033,848494}St. Seira…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849953,850954}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851413,852373}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:13.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852790,853957}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858796,860631}Thank you, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863008,866095}May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875938,877398}A solid-gold statue of Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878273,879650}We don't have any…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879942,881777}All we have are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884238,885989}It's made of solid gold…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886698,888450}Our store doesn't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888534,890077}I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890202,892496}SAKURAI JEWELERS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:57.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894540,897501}We don't have such a thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898293,900379}A solid-gold statue of Mary…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900963,904299}Our store doesn't have it…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904425,905384}Really…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906468,907469}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:12.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907928,912307}That St. Tail! Where is it?\NWhere is the location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:16.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913142,916937}Where in the world is there\Na solid-gold statue of Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921400,922901}Mysterious Thief St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925654,927030}I'm sorry, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:31.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927656,931410}I didn't want you here…\Nwhere she is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936039,938417}I came to get\Nthe statue of Mary back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940961,943505}You came here.\NThat's what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943839,945591}I have several things\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946091,948051}Now watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950012,951889}Doesn't this smell nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953807,956059}Now take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958270,959563}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961231,962649}This fragrance is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966278,967321}The smell in a bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968030,969573}It's lavender!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974578,975871}Your date of birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978582,979625}September…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980501,981668}…29th…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984671,986089}I've heard it somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988175,989843}What is your father's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990594,991720}Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992137,993180}Genichiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993722,994890}And mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996058,997142}Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997518,998560}Eimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001271,1002272}Are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002356,1003815}…the daughter\Nof the Mysterious Thief Lucifer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004942,1006235}Meimi Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007819,1009279}You're Meimi Haneoka,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009446,1011698}You are\Nthe Mysterious Thief St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012324,1013367}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017621,1018956}Meimi Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020457,1021500}Meimi…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021917,1023710}Are you St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023919,1025045}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026255,1027214}You…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027589,1028715}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028799,1030133}Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031635,1033053}Meimi…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035556,1037599}Yes. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038600,1040769}I've been hiding it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041562,1043855}I was scared that you'd find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045649,1047150}I was scared…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048569,1050362}I was really scared…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054116,1055534}Okay. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057286,1059830}I just wanted to know your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:43.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060622,1063250}You said some\Nunexpected things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066336,1067754}Ms. Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069756,1071258}What are you scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071967,1074678}I was hypnotized…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075429,1076471}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:17:59.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078724,1079766}I can't have my secret…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079933,1081268}…revealed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082561,1084187}I wouldn't be able\Nto continue my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085105,1087149}– Your business?\N– That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:11.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087899,1091653}Stealing people's valuables?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097200,1098285}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:22.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098535,1102873}I'm not planning to reveal\Nyour identity to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103582,1106835}Let me tell you what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107044,1108003}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:29.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108462,1109463}I'm thinking of…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110505,1113008}…taking revenge\Non the Mysterious Thief Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114051,1115719}Lucifer…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116094,1117054}My mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117721,1118680}On my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:44.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120307,1124186}Then I'll take the statue\Nof Mary, Ms. St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125354,1126897}You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127856,1129483}One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129650,1130609}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141411,1143080}Oh, the statue of Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143538,1144998}It isn't hot…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146917,1148210}Was it magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156009,1159096}I'll take the statue of Mary,\NMs. Fortune Teller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159513,1160847}How dare you…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161264,1162265}St. Tail…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172234,1173193}What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175404,1176488}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179700,1180659}I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180826,1183328}…what will happen if she\Ncontinues with that business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184079,1185330}Her hypnosis…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:48.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187249,1188792}You're Meimi Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:52.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190419,1192754}I have to stop her hypnosis…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193505,1195716}At the time, my body got cold…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196717,1199302}I thought the real Asuka Jr.\Nwas asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:03.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202764,1203890}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210605,1213567}The solid-gold statue\Nof Mary was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214401,1216403}I'm sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216778,1218155}It was the most valuable item…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218321,1219990}…out of everything\Nwe've gotten recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220741,1222200}– Maju.\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223034,1225662}Lucifer is living a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225829,1227914}It won't be fun to make her suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228290,1229624}Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230125,1231877}What…? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:35.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232919,1235797}And the daughter's pain\Nis her mother's pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236381,1238175}Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238550,1240469}Yes! I'm with you all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240594,1241553}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243472,1246683}We can have\Nmore fun that way, Maju.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248268,1250103}The Mysterious Thief St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250729,1252689}The battle is just now starting…
